          <text><![CDATA[<p>This bill amends the Native American Graves Protection and Repatriation Act to: (1) increase fines on museums that violate such Act, and (2) transfer enforcement of the Act to the Bureau of Indian Affairs.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2018-07-31T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
        </item>
